window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The crime of the century. Admittance by invitation only. Black tie required.</b></p> <p>Dr. Zlo has made some nefarious new associates. After his grand scheme was directly blocked by Vert so that the game would \"make sense\", the deadly and beautiful Dextra Black signed on to help him get his revenge.</p> <p>Although Dr. Zlo has made enemies with popular players and old friends, his zany streaming has captured the attention of thousands. Thanks to the limelight, gamers new and old are joining in just to hunt him down. He knows exactly what to do to keep them entertained; and his grand event won’t just show the world Vert’s true colors. If all goes as planned, they’ll convince people to start playing just for fun.</p> <p>What's that in the sky? A bird? A plane? No! It's <i>evil</i>!</p>"; 
